Ah, I bet she's busy though...
Isn't her big concert coming up
sometime soon?

rows.label: qst201626_msg0004
rows.name:
I'd hoped to show her how much
I've grown as a musician...

rows.label: qst201626_msg0006
rows.name:
But... There's no guaranteeing
that she'll listen to me...

rows.label: qst201626_msg0007
rows.name: Still, I guess it can't hurt to try.

rows.label: qst201626_msg0008
rows.name: Okay! In that case, I'm off!

rows.label: qst201626_msg0009
rows.name:
I've never actually been to
Alba Margen, can you believe?
I wonder what kind of place it is!
